OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FA coin featuring a tiger, a snail and
OL,7,Fa dove has been launched to celebrate
OL,8,F200 years of the Zoological Society of
OL,9,FLondon (ZSL).
OL,11,FThe #2 coin carries the edge
OL,12,Finscription "restoring wildlife
OL,13,Ftogether" and it was created by the
OL,14,FRoyal Mint in collaboration with ZSL.
OL,16,FThe coin was officially launched at
OL,17,FZSL's London Zoo, where a giant wooden
OL,18,Freplica of the coin measuring two
OL,19,Fmetres (6.5ft) in size was given to
OL,20,Fthe conservation zoo's Sumatran tigers
OL,21,Ffor their "roar" of approval.
OL,26,@tD@MOUuD@IO]}D@KOU}D@PO]
