PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FThe replica coin formed part of
OL,7,Factivities which stimulate an animal's
OL,8,Fnatural instincts. For the tigers,
OL,9,Fthis includes stalking and hunting.
OL,11,FThe reverse or "tails" design of the
OL,12,Fcoin brings together three animals
OL,13,Fthat the Mint said "tell a powerful
OL,14,Fstory about ZSL's conservation impact"
OL,15,F` the Sumatran tiger, the Socorro
OL,16,Fdove, and the Partula snail.
OL,26,@sD@POUsD@VO]uD@TOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
