OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FEach is depicted with fine detail,
OL,7,Fincluding the texture of the tiger's
OL,8,Ffur, the delicate feathers of the
OL,9,Fdove, and the ribbed surface of the
OL,10,Fsnail's shell.
OL,12,FBamboo grasses wind between the three
OL,13,Fcreatures, in a nod to the wild
OL,14,Fhabitats ZSL works to protect and
OL,15,Frestore.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
