PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FLucy Mackenzie, director of digital
OL,7,Fand product concept at the Royal Mint,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This coin is so much more than
OL,9,Fa commemorative piece, it's a tribute
OL,10,Fto two centuries of dedication to
OL,11,Fwildlife and our planet.
OL,13,F"We're proud to support ZSL, and every
OL,14,Fpurchase contributes directly to its
OL,15,Fvital environmental work."
OL,17,FShe added: "Being at ZSL's London Zoo
OL,18,Fto officially unveil the coin was a
OL,19,Ftruly special moment.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUwD@ZO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
