PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FKathryn England, ZSL chief executive,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are delighted that ZSL's
OL,8,F200th anniversary is being
OL,9,Fcommemorated with this special #2 coin
OL,10,Ffrom the Royal Mint.
OL,12,F"The design, which highlights three of
OL,13,FZSL's remarkable conservation stories,
OL,14,Freflects just a small part of the
OL,15,Fimpact ZSL has made over the past two
OL,16,Fcenturies.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
