CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FThe coin is available to purchase from
OL,7,Fthe Royal Mint from 9am on Tuesday
OL,8,FApril 14, with prices starting from
OL,9,F#17.50 for a brilliant uncirculated
OL,10,Fversion.
OL,12,FGold and silver versions of the coin
OL,13,Fare also available, with a gold coin
OL,14,Fpriced at #2,505 and silver coins of
OL,15,Fdifferent weights priced at #107.50
OL,16,Fand #190.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
