PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776250558
OL,3,CRoarsome: Giant replica coin unveiled
OL,4,Cat London Zoo to mark 200 years of ZSL
OL,6,FA portion of the net proceeds from
OL,7,Fsales will be donated to ZSL in
OL,8,Fsupport of the charity's global
OL,9,Fconservation work across the world,
OL,10,Fthe Royal Mint said.
OL,12,FFrom May 1, visitors to the Royal Mint
OL,13,FExperience, based in Llantrisant,
OL,14,Fsouth Wales will also be able to
OL,15,Fstrike their own ZSL #2 coin.
